 both the PWIA and FSI expectations at low to medium\nmissing momenta, including the change of the asymmetry due to the contribution\nof the deuteron D-state at higher momenta. At the highest missing momenta, our\ndata clearly agree better with the calculations including FSI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2016 17:06:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-01"}
