th, 17th and 18th September 2013 and we find\n0.67\"/8.9m/3.07m/s of total seeing/outer scale/wind-speed, with\n0.552\"/9.2m/2.89m/s below 1.5 km and 0.263\"/10.3m/5.22m/s between 1.5 and 20\nkm. We have also de- termined the high altitude layers above 20 km, missed by\nthe tomographic reconstruction on Canary , have a median seeing of 0.187\" and\nhave occurred 16% of observation time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 07:50:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-23"}
