xperimental measurements such as inelastic neutron scattering in realistic\nmaterials and complement our theoretical framework, we develop the analytical\ntheory of the dynamical structure factor within the torque equilibrium\nformulism and provide the explicit results of the quasi-one dimensional\n$J_{1}$-$J_{2}$ systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 11:27:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2016 13:59:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-24"}
