alability of our solution. Finally, we show performance improvement\nof 3-140x in PE over commercially available Intel micro-architectures,\nClearSpeed CSX700, FPGA, and Nvidia GPGPUs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2016 12:46:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2016 15:37:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2016 04:26:29 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 14:23:17 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 27 Nov 2016 14:11:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-29"}
